ed="T" n="0856b04"/><persName key="A010594">釋定蘭</persName>，姓<name>楊</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000034805">成都</placeName>人也<ptr target="#n2906"/>。本闤闠<ptr type="glossary" target="#g580"/>間兇惡屠<lb
ed="T" n="0856b05"/>沽類，天與厥性，悔往前非，誓預六和<ptr type="glossary" target="#g25"/>，化行<lb
ed="T" n="0856b06"/><placeName key="PL000000034650">三蜀</placeName>。當爾時也，咸歸信焉。造伽藍一，號<placeName key="PL000000000662">聖<lb
ed="T" n="0856b07"/>壽</placeName>歟。其緣未發，乃藏於傭保中耳。而父母<lb
ed="T" n="0856b08"/>早亡，無資可以追往。每遇諱辰，<persName key="A010594">蘭</persName>悲哭咽<lb
ed="T" n="0856b09"/>絕，輒裸露入<placeName key="PL000000034982">青城山</placeName>，縱蚊蚋䗈蠅唼咋膚<lb
ed="T" n="0856b10"/>體，且云「捨內財<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1901"/>也，用答劬勞<ptr type="glossary" target="#g450"/>。」<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>中有黑白<lb
ed="T" n="0856b11"/>蟆，形如粟，𠯗<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1902"/>人口及肉，而少見者<ptr target="#n2907"/>。次則<lb
ed="T" n="0856b12"/><anchor xml:id="beg0856sgsz11"/>刺<anchor xml:id="end0856sgsz11"/>血寫經，後則<anchor xml:id="beg0856sgsz12"/>煉<anchor xml:id="end0856sgsz12"/>臂，至于拔耳剜目、餧<lb
ed="T" n="0856b13"/>飼鷙鳥<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1121"/>猛獸。既而行步，非扶導而觸物顛<lb
ed="T" n="0856b14"/>躓。後有異人，掌擎物若珠顆然，內空眥<lb
ed="T" n="0856b15"/>中<ptr target="#n2909"/>，斯須瞻矚如故。冥告曰：「<persName key="A018965">南天王</persName>還<ref type="person" target="#A010594">師</ref>眼<lb
ed="T" n="0856b16"/>珠矣。」遠近驚駭。常謂人曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010594">吾</ref>聞《善戒經》中<lb
ed="T" n="0856b17"/>名為無上施<ptr target="#n2908"/>──<ref type="person" target="#A010594">吾</ref>願勤行，速要上果矣。」<date key="j20311832031566" notAfter-iso="+0850-02-19" notBefore-iso="+0849-02-01"><name>大中</name><lb
ed="T" n="0856b18"/>三年</date>，<persName key="A003667">宣宗</persName>詔入內供養，仰其感應之故，以<lb
ed="T" n="0856b19"/>優禮奉之。弟子<persName key="A010592">有緣</persName>，恒執事左右。<date key="j20323052032334" notAfter-iso="+0852-03-28" notBefore-iso="+0852-02-28">六年二<lb
ed="T" n="0856b20"/>月中</date>，又願焚然肩膊。<ref type="person" target="#A003667">帝</ref>累勸勉，年耆且務<lb
ed="T" n="0856b21"/>久長<anchor xml:id="beg0856003"/>修煉<anchor xml:id="end0856003"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g75"/>。<persName key="A010594">蘭</persName>不奉詔，遂焚焉而絕。<persName key="A010592">有緣</persName>表<lb
ed="T" n="0856b22"/>請易名建塔，勅謚<persName key="A010594">覺性</persName>也，塔號<placeName key="PL000000034769">悟真</placeName>也。<lb
ed="T" n="0856b23"/><placeName key="PL000000034805">蜀都</placeName>止呼<placeName key="PL000000034769">定蘭塔院</placeName>，于今香火不絕云。</p>
